Installation 

1. mkdir /tmp/SMPPClient
2. cppy file to directory /tmp/SMPPClient 
3. check perl path in server
4. vi SMPPClient.pl 
   change line 122 and 123 for bind username and password
5. vi SMPPClient , change ip address and port number base on SMSC configuration
6. chmod +x SMPPClient.pl


Test : 

Usage : ./SMPPClient.pl SMPPClient.cfg 886911514571 886936453016 'Test  11'

or 
Usage : perl SMPPClient.pl SMPPClient.cfg 886911514571 886936453016 'Test SMS abc'
